<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Suspension - Your Application</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dddddd;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #333;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .strong {
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .email-footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Account Suspension</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Dear <%= fullname %>,</p>
        <p>
          Your account has been suspended temporary due to the following reason:
        </p>
        <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reason %></p>
        <p>
          If you believe this is a mistake, please contact our support team as
          soon as possible.
        </p>
        <p>Thank you,</p>
        <p>HTU LMS Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">&copy; 2024 HTU LMS. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
